text:
Meet Oregon's high school football all-stars: Les Schwab Bowl 2017 South roster Updated February 23, 2017 Comment LES SCHWAB BOWL 2017 - SOUTH ROSTER 
The 2017 Les Schwab Bowl -- an annual all-star football game featuring many of the state's top graduated seniors -- will take place June 24 at Hillsboro Stadium. 
Here's a look at the players selected for the South roster. ( Click here to meet the North all-stars. ) RUNNING BACKS & DEFENSIVE BACKS Kent Frasure | For The Oregonian/OregonLive JASH ALLEN, TIGARD
